  3. Te3 Chu2 e5 lang5 u7 heng7-hok, <BR>Sui-jian5 kiaN5 ou-am3 soaN-kok; <BR>Na7 te3 Ia5-sou e5 kha-pou7, <BR>Oe7 tit Chu2 ka7 lan2 chhoa7 lou7. <BR>A-men. 
